data.description: What a GEM!  Rare spacious & bright 3 bedroom 2.5 bathroom CORNER UNIT townhome in centrally located Pinebrook Estates! The first floor features an open concept design with a large living room accented by a cozy wood burning fireplace, a dining area, a functional kitchen with breakfast high bar, a powder bathroom for guests, and a conveniently located interior laundry closet.  Just off the kitchen is an enclosed covered porch overlooking the private & fully fenced backyard.  Wooden staircase leads up to the second floor featuring 3 bedrooms with vaulted ceilings, and 2 full bathrooms. Plenty of storage and closet space throughout this home including bonus storage under the stairs & on the covered porch.  Parking is easy with one reserved parking spot & plenty of visitor spaces.  Recent updates include brand new electrical panel 2023. New HVAC 2021.  New Water Heater 2020. Fresh interior paint in some of the rooms. New living room blinds. The HOA replaced the roof in 2023.  Community has a pool and handball courts.  Low HOA fee includes exterior maintenance, community pool, grounds maintenance and lawn care.  Conveniently located in the heart of Pinellas County - this central location can't be beat and is close to everything...shopping, restaurants, world class beaches, sporting events, downtown St. Pete or Tampa, short ride to the airports, interstates, parks, entertainment, and so much more!  This is a fantastic opportunity to own a large & spacious townhome in a great community with low HOA dues!  Schedule your showing today! Home is part of a guardianship sale which is subject to court approval.
